01:01:36.551 --> 01:01:37.292
Bring a prayer.

01:01:40.497 --> 01:01:43.602
I know we've already said a prayer, but I want to pray a specific prayer for you.

01:01:44.258 --> 01:01:47.383
because I know it took a lot of courage to step out of that seat.

01:01:47.403 --> 01:01:49.105
I don't know your story, but God does.

01:01:49.986 --> 01:01:52.050
I don't know what brought you to this place, but God does.

01:01:52.891 --> 01:01:53.572
And he's got you.

01:01:54.593 --> 01:01:59.240
And he's gonna help you through these next few days and weeks with the challenges in your life.

01:01:59.320 --> 01:02:05.429
And so Father, I thank you for every single child, mom, dad, individual who's made a decision today.

01:02:05.489 --> 01:02:06.771
I pray that they would walk with you.

01:02:07.312 --> 01:02:08.233
They would treasure you.

01:02:08.374 --> 01:02:11.378
You would help them, Father God, every day of their life.

01:02:11.682 --> 01:02:15.026
Even the moments they don't understand you would draw close to them, Father.

01:02:15.587 --> 01:02:18.310
I thank you that the 1st of February is a life-changing date.

01:02:19.151 --> 01:02:20.113
In Jesus' name.

01:02:21.114 --> 01:02:21.554
Amen.

01:02:22.135 --> 01:02:22.476
Amen.

01:02:23.777 --> 01:02:24.919
This is Annie just here.

01:02:24.939 --> 01:02:25.620
Give us a wave, Annie.

01:02:26.341 --> 01:02:27.442
We're going to give you a little gift.

01:02:27.502 --> 01:02:28.944
It's a Bible, OK?

01:02:28.964 --> 01:02:30.145
So we've got a little quiet chap.

01:02:30.165 --> 01:02:33.710
We're going to give you the Bible, give you some next steps, and then you're going to jump straight back.

01:02:33.730 --> 01:02:35.893
But I'm also going to come off the stage and shake your hand.

01:02:35.953 --> 01:02:36.433
Is that all right?

01:02:36.453 --> 01:02:39.217
Because I want to congratulate you on this incredible decision.

01:02:39.257 --> 01:02:40.178
So head this way with me.

01:02:41.730 --> 01:02:43.012
Thanks again for tuning in.

01:02:43.733 --> 01:02:56.130
If you said yes to Jesus today by saying the Salvation Prayer, we'd love for you to email connections at soulchurch.com, so we can talk to you a little bit more about this incredible decision you've just made.

01:02:56.771 --> 01:03:04.562
And if at any point in the service, you felt moved to give towards any of our local or global initiatives, head to soulchurch.com.

01:03:05.026 --> 01:03:12.031
And don't forget to stay connected with us on Facebook, Instagram, and YouTube by searching at Soul Church UK.

01:03:12.633 --> 01:03:14.098
Take care and God bless.

